00:29:07,270 --> 00:29:08,720
But in short,

567
00:29:09,220 --> 00:29:11,180
you've been deceived.

568
00:29:11,900 --> 00:29:13,700
Not to mention
for the past two and a half years,

569
00:29:13,700 --> 00:29:15,190
you've been the backbone

570
00:29:15,240 --> 00:29:18,240
of Macau's anti-Japanese
underground supply line,

571
00:29:18,660 --> 00:29:21,590
just this smuggling case
with Steamship Sai On alone

572
00:29:21,820 --> 00:29:22,950
is already backed by

573
00:29:23,510 --> 00:29:24,900
ironclad evidence.

574
00:29:26,050 --> 00:29:27,850
And once the verdict is reached,

575
00:29:27,930 --> 00:29:31,970
we Japanese have the right to demand
extradition of the principal offender.

576
00:29:31,970 --> 00:29:35,200
When that happens, let alone
the Portuguese Macau government—

577
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:36,880
even if Lisbon steps in,

578
00:29:37,090 --> 00:29:38,770
they won't be able to protect you,

579
00:29:38,770 --> 00:29:40,140
Mr. He Xian.

580
00:29:47,550 --> 00:29:49,830
Colonel Sawa, since you keep saying

581
00:29:50,010 --> 00:29:52,530
there are both witnesses
and physical evidence,

582
00:29:52,530 --> 00:29:55,240
then why waste your breath
talking to me here?

583
00:29:55,940 --> 00:29:56,970
I just...

584
00:29:58,340 --> 00:30:00,740
Feel sorry to lose someone
of your caliber.

585
00:30:01,900 --> 00:30:03,900
I wanted to give you a way out.

586
00:30:04,370 --> 00:30:05,540
Is that so?

587
00:30:06,530 --> 00:30:09,610
Haven't you been dreaming of
destroying me, Colonel Sawa?

588
00:30:09,610 --> 00:30:11,410
Now that the chance has arrived,

589
00:30:11,470 --> 00:30:13,530
why are you suddenly being so polite?

590
00:30:14,690 --> 00:30:15,580
Let me

591
00:30:15,890 --> 00:30:17,230
guess the reason.

592
00:30:17,660 --> 00:30:20,310
That captured suspect from Zhongshan
you mentioned

593
00:30:20,310 --> 00:30:22,010
only has hearsay evidence

594
00:30:22,420 --> 00:30:25,050
and has never directly dealt with
the Macau government.

595
00:30:25,050 --> 00:30:27,350
You can't possibly convict
the Macau government

596
00:30:27,350 --> 00:30:29,650
based on just a secondhand testimony.

597
00:30:30,250 --> 00:30:30,970
That's why

598
00:30:31,450 --> 00:30:34,180
you wanted to use me,
someone directly involved,

599
00:30:34,460 --> 00:30:36,720
to falsely accuse the Macau government,

600
00:30:36,870 --> 00:30:38,210
so as to charge the Macau government

601
00:30:38,210 --> 00:30:39,960
with violating neutrality

602
00:30:40,000 --> 00:30:41,660
and participating in the war.

603
00:30:42,290 --> 00:30:43,290
Isn't that right?

604
00:30:47,410 --> 00:30:48,470
Whatever the case,

605
00:30:50,010 --> 00:30:51,540
if you refuse to cooperate,

606
00:30:52,460 --> 00:30:54,310
you'll die a horrible death.

607
00:30:58,090 --> 00:30:59,420
You know perfectly well

608
00:30:59,740 --> 00:31:01,860
how the Portuguese Macau government

609
00:31:01,890 --> 00:31:04,020
has been treating you Chinese people.

610
00:31:05,840 --> 00:31:07,290
I just don't understand

611
00:31:07,520 --> 00:31:09,150
why you feel the need

612
00:31:09,180 --> 00:31:10,680
to be their scapegoat.

613
00:31:11,540 --> 00:31:12,750
To protect them,

614
00:31:12,790 --> 00:31:15,270
you're even willing to risk your own life

615
00:31:15,270 --> 00:31:17,610
and your entire family's future.

616
00:31:21,220 --> 00:31:22,880
Alright, that's all I'll say.

617
00:31:22,890 --> 00:31:24,850
When talking to a smart person,

618
00:31:25,290 --> 00:31:27,700
a hint is enough.

619
00:31:28,980 --> 00:31:32,110
There're two paths before you right now.

620
00:31:32,700 --> 00:31:34,250
One is to confess the truth,

621
00:31:35,820 --> 00:31:37,160
and our Empire of Japan

622
00:31:37,190 --> 00:31:39,250
will guarantee you a secure position

623
00:31:39,330 --> 00:31:41,930
at the very top of
Macau's business community.

624
00:31:42,050 --> 00:31:43,010
And the second

625
00:31:44,420 --> 00:31:45,920
is to remain obstinate—

626
00:31:46,720 --> 00:31:48,310
as for how that path ends,

627
00:31:50,680 --> 00:31:52,390
you know very well yourself.

628
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,160
What's with that laugh?

629
00:31:59,160 --> 00:32:00,470
I was laughing because Colonel Sawa,

630
00:32:00,470 --> 00:32:02,340
you really are quite the schemer.

631
00:32:02,840 --> 00:32:05,640
Forcing me to falsely accuse
the Macau government

632
00:32:06,200 --> 00:32:08,280
to give you a good excuse

633
00:32:08,310 --> 00:32:09,850
for your armed occupation of Macau.

634
00:32:09,850 --> 00:32:12,050
And once I betray the Macau government,

635
00:32:12,100 --> 00:32:14,490
I'll have no way back.

636
00:32:15,130 --> 00:32:17,390
I can only willingly become a traitor

637
00:32:17,410 --> 00:32:19,080
to serve you Japanese

638
00:32:19,100 --> 00:32:21,490
and provide you with endless supplies.

639
00:32:21,800 --> 00:32:23,560
My life

640
00:32:23,580 --> 00:32:25,070
in exchange for the entire Macau

641
00:32:25,070 --> 00:32:27,330
and the countless supplies you dream of—

642
00:32:27,830 --> 00:32:30,440
what a profitable deal indeed.

643
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:32,050
If you don't cooperate,

644
00:32:36,450 --> 00:32:37,490
you're finished.

645
00:32:38,890 --> 00:32:42,230
Your underground supply network
will be finished as well.

646
00:32:42,830 --> 00:32:44,290
You're doomed either way.

647
00:32:44,960 --> 00:32:46,280
The only difference is

648
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:48,540
whether you want to save yourself

649
00:32:48,650 --> 00:32:50,860
or those Portuguese.

650
00:32:55,130 --> 00:32:57,420
It's clearly a losing deal,

651
00:32:57,440 --> 00:32:58,580
so why would you

652
00:32:59,010 --> 00:33:01,270
go down with those Portuguese

653
00:33:01,300 --> 00:33:03,300
who can offer you nothing in return?

654
00:33:08,850 --> 00:33:10,110
In your view,

655
00:33:10,630 --> 00:33:12,420
anyone who does anything

656
00:33:12,750 --> 00:33:14,080
only does it to gain

657
00:33:14,360 --> 00:33:16,290
greater benefits for themselves.

658
00:33:16,290 --> 00:33:17,290
Isn't that right?

659
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:19,390
What else

660
00:33:20,580 --> 00:33:21,980
could it possibly be for?

661
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:23,440
That's why

662
00:33:24,100 --> 00:33:25,640
you'll never understand.

663
00:33:26,760 --> 00:33:29,540
Because bandits are always
blinded by greed,

664
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:31,630
and people like you

665
00:33:32,030 --> 00:33:34,090
know nothing but threats and bribes.

666
00:33:36,190 --> 00:33:36,920
Alright.

667
00:33:37,600 --> 00:33:39,060
I've said all I have to say.

668
00:33:39,790 --> 00:33:42,850
If you think I'll falsely accuse
the Macau government,

669
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:44,600
you've miscalculated.

670
00:33:45,540 --> 00:33:48,670
When there's a road to Heaven,
you refuse to take it;

671
00:33:49,530 --> 00:33:52,900
and when there's no gate to hell,
you walk right in.

672
00:33:53,610 --> 00:33:54,670
He Xian,

673
00:33:55,200 --> 00:33:55,900
then

674
00:33:56,950 --> 00:33:59,010
don't blame me for what happens next.

675
00:34:01,010 --> 00:34:02,060
Yamaguchi.

676
00:34:06,770 --> 00:34:07,470
Yes, Sir.

677
00:34:07,550 --> 00:34:09,679
Notify Lin Nianci in Zhongshan County

678
00:34:09,739 --> 00:34:11,820
to immediately bring
the prisoner Liang Zhong

679
00:34:11,820 --> 00:34:13,760
and his detailed confession

680
00:34:14,110 --> 00:34:15,420
to Macau.

681
00:34:16,090 --> 00:34:16,620
Yes, Sir.

682
00:34:31,580 --> 00:34:32,520
Dr. Ke,

683
00:34:32,960 --> 00:34:34,210
how is Captain Long?

684
00:34:35,090 --> 00:34:36,420
She's out of danger now.

685
00:34:36,900 --> 00:34:38,500
She should be able to pull through.

686
00:34:38,500 --> 00:34:39,760
What about Zhengping?

687
00:34:42,010 --> 00:34:43,030
He's in the ward.

688
00:34:43,250 --> 00:34:45,980
He'll probably need one or two months
to recover.

689
00:34:46,659 --> 00:34:47,929
Any news on your end?

690
00:34:47,949 --> 00:34:50,110
Lok Pak called an hour ago.

691
00:34:50,429 --> 00:34:52,260
Sawa Eisaku has ordered Zhongshan

692
00:34:52,260 --> 00:34:54,460
to transfer Mr. Liang and his confession
to Macau.

693
00:34:54,460 --> 00:34:56,620
Yang Chang has urgently notified
Commander Ou.

694
00:34:56,620 --> 00:34:59,080
He said he'll do everything he can
to stop it,

695
00:34:59,460 --> 00:35:00,860
but there's no guarantee

696
00:35:01,290 --> 00:35:02,150
he'll succeed.

697
00:35:05,040 --> 00:35:06,890
What about Xian? Where is he?

698
00:35:08,180 --> 00:35:10,640
He was taken by
the Portuguese authorities.

699
00:35:13,020 --> 00:35:14,080
I understand.

700
00:35:15,670 --> 00:35:17,670
It seems that this time,

701
00:35:18,810 --> 00:35:21,270
whether Xian and Macau
can get through this crisis

702
00:35:21,270 --> 00:35:22,730
is up to Commander Ou.

703
00:35:27,650 --> 00:35:30,710
What should we do with this little one,
Magistrate Lin?

704
00:35:31,250 --> 00:35:32,110
Take him along.

705
00:35:38,730 --> 00:35:41,530
When we get to Macau,
if you recant your confession

706
00:35:41,730 --> 00:35:43,690
or say anything you shouldn't,

707
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:46,210
as for your precious grandson,

708
00:35:46,210 --> 00:35:47,410
I'll immediately...

709
00:35:47,590 --> 00:35:48,390
Rest assured.

710
00:35:48,650 --> 00:35:49,490
Rest assured.

711
00:35:49,820 --> 00:35:51,180
I won't say anything.

712
00:35:51,200 --> 00:35:52,320
Not a word.

713
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:54,230
Let's go.

714
00:36:11,740 --> 00:36:14,340
Chief, we received a telegram
from Zhongshan.

715
00:36:16,000 --> 00:36:16,900
Mr. He.

716
00:36:18,020 --> 00:36:19,260
I have news for you.

717
00:36:19,990 --> 00:36:22,520
Lin Nianci,
Magistrate of Zhongshan County,

718
00:36:22,740 --> 00:36:25,650
has already departed with the prisoner.

719
00:36:26,830 --> 00:36:28,630
It's now 6:30.

720
00:36:29,050 --> 00:36:30,420
By 7:00 at the latest,

721
00:36:31,150 --> 00:36:34,480
they will rendezvous with
the Imperial Army's escort ship.

722
00:36:35,150 --> 00:36:36,690
I have to warn you.

723
00:36:37,380 --> 00:36:40,460
Once the suspect
is handed over to the navy,

724
00:36:40,720 --> 00:36:42,740
it'll be out of my control.

725
00:36:43,090 --> 00:36:43,990
So,

726
00:36:45,030 --> 00:36:46,740
you have at most

727
00:36:47,710 --> 00:36:49,150
half an hour left.

728
00:36:49,890 --> 00:36:52,750
It's your last chance to tell

729
00:36:53,510 --> 00:36:55,740
the truth about Steamship Sai On.

730
00:37:06,510 --> 00:37:07,050
Alright.

731
00:37:07,940 --> 00:37:08,750
I'll say it.

732
00:37:09,820 --> 00:37:10,820
Good.

733
00:37:11,210 --> 00:37:13,110
You're finally willing to talk.

734
00:37:14,200 --> 00:37:15,330
Go ahead and tell me.

735
00:37:15,550 --> 00:37:17,070
It's not too late yet.

736
00:37:17,320 --> 00:37:18,650
But we're in Macau now,

737
00:37:18,670 --> 00:37:21,250
and I rented Steamship Sai On
from the Macau government.

738
00:37:21,250 --> 00:37:21,930
Therefore,

739
00:37:22,150 --> 00:37:24,280
I'll only confess to the Macau police.

740
00:37:25,650 --> 00:37:27,380
Inspector General Gonçalves.

741
00:37:30,170 --> 00:37:30,940
Mr. He.

742
00:37:31,400 --> 00:37:33,320
Please have all irrelevant personnel leave

743
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:34,620
and turn off the surveillance.

744
00:37:34,620 --> 00:37:35,850
I'll tell only you.

745
00:37:37,560 --> 00:37:38,360
Colonel Sawa.

746
00:37:39,020 --> 00:37:39,890
No.

747
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:43,920
This is a Japanese-Portuguese
joint investigation.

748
00:37:43,920 --> 00:37:46,110
I must know the suspect's statement.

749
00:37:46,990 --> 00:37:48,730
But this is still Macau,

750
00:37:48,760 --> 00:37:50,300
and even in a joint investigation,

751
00:37:50,300 --> 00:37:52,890
the Macau police have priority.

752
00:37:53,030 --> 00:37:55,800
Colonel Sawa,
if you don't want to solve this case,

753
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,860
then by all means, keep wasting time.

754
00:38:05,230 --> 00:38:05,890
Wait.

755
00:38:08,800 --> 00:38:09,440
Fine.

756
00:38:11,330 --> 00:38:12,400
At this point,

757
00:38:14,550 --> 00:38:17,630
I doubt you can pull any tricks anyway.

758
00:38:20,120 --> 00:38:20,810
I'll leave.

759
00:38:45,080 --> 00:38:46,030
Governor,

760
00:38:46,030 --> 00:38:47,480
He Xian has just confessed

761
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:49,340
who the real owner of
the smuggled diesel is.

762
00:38:49,340 --> 00:38:50,000
Who is it?

763
00:38:50,550 --> 00:38:53,920
I'm sorry, but the suspect's confession
may not be accurate.

764
00:38:53,920 --> 00:38:55,810
The police need to further investigate
and gather evidence,

765
00:38:55,810 --> 00:38:57,580
and after confirming the authenticity
of the confession,

766
00:38:57,580 --> 00:38:59,870
we will inform you of the results.

767
00:39:00,050 --> 00:39:01,010
Your Excellency the Governor,

768
00:39:01,010 --> 00:39:02,670
I request permission to lead a team

769
00:39:02,670 --> 00:39:04,380
to arrest the smuggling suspect
named by He Xian

770
00:39:04,380 --> 00:39:05,070
to verify the truth.

771
00:39:05,070 --> 00:39:06,910
You have my permission.
Take action immediately.

772
00:39:06,910 --> 00:39:07,440
Yes, Sir.

773
00:39:22,260 --> 00:39:22,990
Boss!

774
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:25,320
What's wrong? Don't panic.

775
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:26,980
Take your time. What happened?

776
00:39:26,980 --> 00:39:27,860
Bad news!

777
00:39:27,860 --> 00:39:28,730
Something bad happened!

778
00:39:28,730 --> 00:39:29,660
What happened?

779
00:39:30,090 --> 00:39:33,070
I just called Tai Fung Bank
and the He family to follow up,

780
00:39:33,070 --> 00:39:36,360
only to learn that
He Xian was arrested last night.

781
00:39:36,360 --> 00:39:37,530
Arrested?

782
00:39:37,530 --> 00:39:38,460
What's going on?

783
00:39:38,650 --> 00:39:41,730
He was arrested by the Macau police
and Agency Chief Sawa together.

784
00:39:41,730 --> 00:39:42,490
I heard

785
00:39:42,890 --> 00:39:44,880
it was because of
the Steamship Sai On's...

786
00:39:44,880 --> 00:39:46,600
Something like a diesel smuggling case.

787
00:39:46,600 --> 00:39:47,870
Steamship Sai On?

788
00:39:48,110 --> 00:39:49,490
But I've checked the diesel.

789
00:39:49,490 --> 00:39:49,670
[No smoking or fire in the warehouse]

790
00:39:49,670 --> 00:39:50,550
Check again.

791
00:39:54,520 --> 00:39:54,830
It's correct. This is indeed diesel.

792
00:39:54,830 --> 00:39:56,340
[No smoking or fire in the warehouse]

793
00:39:56,340 --> 00:39:57,030
Boss!

794
00:39:57,360 --> 00:39:57,880
But over here...

795
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:59,320
What I have here is water!

796
00:40:00,590 --> 00:40:01,780
He Xian...

797
00:40:02,140 --> 00:40:03,940
That bastard. He set us up.

798
00:40:03,970 --> 00:40:06,050
He switched it to water to scam us!

799
00:40:06,780 --> 00:40:08,650
Don't move! Nobody move!

800
00:40:08,650 --> 00:40:09,400
Police anti-smuggling raid!

801
00:40:09,400 --> 00:40:10,920
Oh, Officer Gonçalves...

802
00:40:11,670 --> 00:40:13,780
Watch out! The suspect's armed

803
00:40:13,860 --> 00:40:15,860
and suspected of resisting arrest!

804
00:40:16,810 --> 00:40:21,600
[Herbal Tea Shop]

805
00:40:32,230 --> 00:40:36,090
[Zhang's Ship Supplies Shop]

806
00:41:12,530 --> 00:41:14,700
Magistrate Lin! Magistrate Lin!

807
00:41:14,730 --> 00:41:15,820
What should we do?

808
00:41:15,870 --> 00:41:18,360
Is it the Tai Ho Brotherhood
and the guerrillas?

809
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:19,540
How would I know?

810
00:41:20,020 --> 00:41:22,350
We'll be shot full of holes
if we stay here!

811
00:41:22,650 --> 00:41:24,450
Quick, retreat toward the pier!

812
00:41:29,680 --> 00:41:30,710
Grandpa!

813
00:41:47,500 --> 00:41:48,690
Grandpa!

814
00:42:21,750 --> 00:42:22,670
This is

815
00:42:22,700 --> 00:42:24,480
what we found in the warehouse.

816
00:42:24,900 --> 00:42:27,580
This is the diesel purchase contract

817
00:42:27,610 --> 00:42:30,000
between Wang Qizheng and He Xian.

818
00:42:30,130 --> 00:42:31,390
It was signed 3 days ago.

819
00:42:31,390 --> 00:42:33,310
And this is the receipt for
Wang Qizheng's payment

820
00:42:33,310 --> 00:42:35,440
to He Xian for renting Steamship Sai On.

821
00:42:35,440 --> 00:42:36,550
And this is a secret agreement

822
00:42:36,550 --> 00:42:38,840
for the private sale of diesel
between Wang Qizheng

823
00:42:38,840 --> 00:42:40,970
and Zhongshan County Magistrate,
Lin Nianci.

824
00:42:40,970 --> 00:42:42,100
All these prove that

825
00:42:42,110 --> 00:42:44,810
He Xian did sell the diesel
before the declaration period ended

826
00:42:44,810 --> 00:42:46,290
and rented the ship

827
00:42:46,320 --> 00:42:47,330
on behalf of his client.

828
00:42:47,330 --> 00:42:47,580
[No smoking or fire in the warehouse]

829
00:42:47,580 --> 00:42:48,880
It's considered legal operation.

830
00:42:48,880 --> 00:42:50,670
While the one who evaded declaration,
secretly smuggled,

831
00:42:50,670 --> 00:42:51,760
got caught by the police,

832
00:42:51,760 --> 00:42:53,610
and even assaulted officers during arrest,
was Wang Qizheng.

833
00:42:53,610 --> 00:42:54,950
The target of his smuggling

834
00:42:54,950 --> 00:42:56,790
was Zhongshan County Magistrate,
Lin Nianci.

835
00:42:56,790 --> 00:42:59,290
[No smoking or fire in the warehouse]

836
00:42:59,290 --> 00:43:00,250
It's fake.

837
00:43:01,670 --> 00:43:04,890
This is complete nonsense.
